EXTRACTED VALUE: "And it's getting deeper the farther we go," replied Marshall. "At some point, this branch pipe must have been filled with water."
I stop, and there’s a polite silence. My face is prickling. “It, um, it is very . . .”
"I mean, you know, is she in shape?"
Myron felt his legs buckle a bit. He let himself land on the chaise.
“Mm. At least in here they’re too old to leap up and down.”
